Per Tho: Ashe, Graijens. Reports. Selections. Latin and English Coke, Edward, Sir, 1552-1634. Ashe, Thomas, fl. 1600-1618.

Latin quotations with English translations. Enlarged from the final "collection" in STC 5525. Signatures: A-O. With coat of arms on verso of first leaf and final errata leaf. Last two leaves are blank. A variant--lacks comma after title word "Knight". Reproduction of original in the Cambridge University Library, Cambridge, England.
